{"type":null,"faqId":14627,"title":"彩信发送或接收失败，如何解决？","answer":"<p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:56.75pt;text-indent:-14.2pt;line-height:12.0pt;tab-stops:list 42.55pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\"><span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;\nfont-family:Wingdings;position:relative;top:-1.0pt;\"><span>l<span style=\"font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">数据业务关闭时，无法发送和接收彩信。发送和下载彩信前，请先连接移动网络。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:56.75pt;text-indent:-14.2pt;line-height:12.0pt;tab-stops:list 42.55pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\"><span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;\nfont-family:Wingdings;position:relative;top:-1.0pt;\"><span>l<span style=\"font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">附件大小超过</span><span> 300KB </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">则无法发送，建议您拆分为多封彩信发送或更换其他发送方式。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:56.75pt;text-indent:-14.2pt;line-height:12.0pt;tab-stops:list 42.55pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\"><span style=\"font-size:8.0pt;\nfont-family:Wingdings;position:relative;top:-1.0pt;\"><span>l<span style=\"font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'\">&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">若在连接移动网络的情况下仍然无法发送和接收彩信，请检查手机是否有足够的可用存储空间。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:2.0cm;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\n\">进入<b>设置</b>界面，点击<b>存储</b>查看可用空间。若空间不足，可点击相应条目查看已用空间，并清理一些文件释放足够的存储空间。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:42.55pt;line-height:12.0pt;page-break-after:avoid;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\"><span><img width=\"557\" height=\"300\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20140828172406586001.gif\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:42.55pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:2.0cm;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\"><span>* </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\n\">图示仅供参考，具体操作请以手机实际界面为准。</span></p>\n<br>\n</p>","faqTypeId":136,"faqType":"信息与邮件","useful":2,"unUseful":2,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"6669","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-SMS-Email","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1409217849000,"seriesProductName":"Holly-T00,Holly-U10","visitedTimes":182,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}